---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro">

  <!-- ENGLISH -->
  <div class="lang-en">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>13+ years building installed capacity in social organizations, rural ventures and communities across Costa Rica and Central America.</p>
      </div>

      <section class="bio">
        <p class="section-tag">Profile</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">About me</h2>
        <div class="bio-content">
        <img class="about-portrait" src="/img/profile-portrait.jpg" alt="Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro" />
                  <div>
            <p>I am a Contador Privado Incorporado (CPI), Tax Advisor and hold a Master in Financial Management. Through JP Asesores, my professional practice in Costa Rica, I work with social organizations, communities and institutions on data, evidence and territorial intelligence.</p>
            <p>My work centers on innovation, data science, impact evaluation and territorial intelligence, with a growing focus on applied AI for social and collective good, data sovereignty, and education. Every project is a chance to build tools that stay in the territory.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>I coordinate the Nosara Community Census 2024, the first district-level census in Costa Rica, and I lead the Alliance for Community Development (ADC) in Nosara. I am also the author of the Nosara District Territorial Fiscal Balance, the country's first subnational fiscal study.</p>
            <p>I work in English and Spanish, with experience across international cooperation, foundations, private philanthropy and corporate social responsibility throughout Central America.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="creds">
        <p class="section-tag">Education</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Education & certifications</h2>
        <div class="cred-list">
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Master in Financial Management</h4><p>Euncet Business School, Barcelona, Spain (2019)</p></div></div>
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Specialization in Financial Management</h4><p>The George Washington University, Washington D.C., USA (2019)</p></div></div>
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Contador Privado Incorporado (CPI) & Tax Advisor</h4><p>Member of the Costa Rican Association of Private Accountants (Colegio de Contadores Privados)</p></div></div>
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Small Business Development Center (SBDC) certification</h4><p>Joint program by INA, MEIC and the U.S. Embassy</p></div></div>
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Advanced English Program</h4><p>Costa Rican North American Cultural Center (CCCN)</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="projects">
        <p class="section-tag">Experience</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Selected achievements</h2>
        <div class="project-list">
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Nosara Community Census</h3><p>Coordination of the first district-level census in Costa Rica. USD 120,000 raised plus USD 50,000 in-kind. Technical advisory from INEC, 95.1% household coverage.</p></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Nosara Territorial Fiscal Balance</h3><p>Authored the first district-level fiscal study in Costa Rica. Fiscal gap above USD 55M per year, cadastral gap factor of 12.1x, 96.6% informal lodging identified.</p></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - 2020</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Entrepreneurship, innovation &amp; early-stage support</h3><p>13 years of experience in entrepreneurship, innovation and early-stage venture support. Program Coordinator at Yo Emprendedor 2013-2020.</p></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - now</div><div class="project-info"><h3>JP Asesores S.R.L.</h3><p>Director and Senior Consultant. 60+ social organizations and SMEs served in financial sustainability, business plans, financial models and tax advisory.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ESPANOL -->
  <div class="lang-es">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Trayectoria</h1>
        <p>Mas de 13 anos construyendo capacidad instalada en organizaciones sociales, emprendimientos rurales y comunidades de Costa Rica y Centroamerica.</p>
      </div>

      <section class="bio">
        <p class="section-tag">Perfil</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Sobre mi</h2>
        <div class="bio-content">
        <img class="about-portrait" src="/img/profile-portrait.jpg" alt="Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro" />
                  <div>
            <p>Soy Contador Privado Incorporado, Asesor Tributario y Master en Administracion Financiera. Desde JP Asesores, mi practica profesional en Costa Rica, trabajo con organizaciones sociales, comunidades e instituciones en datos, evidencia e inteligencia territorial.</p>
            <p>Mi trabajo se centra en innovacion, ciencia de datos, evaluacion de impacto e inteligencia territorial, con un foco creciente en inteligencia artificial aplicada a lo social y colectivo, soberania de datos y educacion. Cada proyecto es una oportunidad de brindar herramientas que se queden en el territorio.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>Coordino el Censo Comunitario de Nosara 2024, el primer censo a nivel de distrito en Costa Rica, y lidero la Alianza para el Desarrollo Comunitario (ADC) en Nosara. Tambien soy autor del Balance Fiscal Territorial del Distrito de Nosara, el primer estudio fiscal subnacional del pais.</p>
            <p>Trabajo en espanol e ingles, y tengo experiencia con cooperacion internacional, fundaciones, filantropia privada y RSE corporativa en toda la region centroamericana.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="creds">
        <p class="section-tag">Formacion</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Educacion y certificaciones</h2>
        <div class="cred-list">
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Master en Administracion Financiera</h4><p>Euncet Business School, Barcelona, Espana (2019)</p></div></div>
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Especializacion en Administracion Financiera</h4><p>The George Washington University, Washington D.C., EEUU (2019)</p></div></div>
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Contador Privado Incorporado (CPI) y Asesor Tributario</h4><p>Colegiado al Colegio de Contadores Privados de Costa Rica</p></div></div>
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Certificacion Small Business Development Center (SBDC)</h4><p>Programa conjunto INA, MEIC y Embajada de los Estados Unidos</p></div></div>
          <div class="cred-item"><div class="cred-dot"></div><div><h4>Programa Avanzado de Ingles</h4><p>Centro Cultural Costarricense Norteamericano (CCCN)</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="projects">
        <p class="section-tag">Experiencia</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Logros destacados</h2>
        <div class="project-list">
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Censo Comunitario de Nosara</h3><p>Coordinacion del primer censo a nivel de distrito en Costa Rica. USD 120,000 en fondos gestionados mas USD 50,000 en aportes en especie. Asesoria tecnica del INEC, 95.1% de cobertura de hogares.</p></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Balance Fiscal Territorial de Nosara</h3><p>Autoria del primer estudio fiscal a nivel de distrito en Costa Rica. Brecha fiscal cuantificada superior a USD 55 millones anuales, factor de brecha catastral de 12.1x, 96.6% de alojamientos informales identificados.</p></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - 2020</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Emprendimiento, innovacion y apoyo a proyectos en fase temprana</h3><p>13 anos de experiencia en emprendimiento, innovacion y apoyo a proyectos en fase temprana. Coordinador de Programas en Yo Emprendedor 2013-2020.</p></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - hoy</div><div class="project-info"><h3>JP Asesores S.R.L.</h3><p>Director y Consultor Senior. Mas de 60 organizaciones sociales y PYMEs atendidas en sostenibilidad financiera, planes de negocio, modelos financieros y acompanamiento tributario.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
